我们就来次真正的火车旅行
we're gonna take a real train ride

1099
01:10:49,200 --> 01:10:53,160
走遍大江南北直到我们精疲力尽
all the way across the country till we can't go no more.

1100
01:10:53,410 --> 01:10:55,690
我在书上读到俄勒冈州涨潮期的海洋最美最蓝
I read where they got this great blue ocean up in oregon.

1101
01:10:55,940 --> 01:10:58,460
这东西大到你无法想象
I mean, this thing's so big and wide,

1102
01:10:58,710 --> 01:10:59,850
一望无际
you can't even see the other side.

1103
01:11:03,460 --> 01:11:05,680
你哭了?
You cryin'?

1104
01:11:05,930 --> 01:11:08,890
为什么?
What on earth for?

1105
01:11:09,140 --> 01:11:12,330
我只想知道为何选择我作为你漫长旅途的伴侣
Just wonderin' where I fit in on this long list of conquests.

1106
01:11:16,040 --> 01:11:18,150
我美丽 甜蜜的宝贝
My beautiful, sweet darlin'.

1107
01:11:18,740 --> 01:11:20,520
你觉得我是在玩弄你?
You think I'm toyin' with you?

1108
01:11:20,770 --> 01:11:23,860
我不知该作何感想
I don't know what to think.

1109
01:11:24,110 --> 01:11:25,820
这是我的初夜
This is my first time.

1110
01:11:27,110 --> 01:11:29,630
我一直想留给我未来的丈夫
I was savin' myself for a husband,

1111
01:11:29,880 --> 01:11:31,700
就像上帝告诉我那样
just like god told me to.

1112
01:11:31,950 --> 01:11:34,300
我是认真的 罗斯安娜
I ain't foolin' here, roseanna.

1113
01:11:34,550 --> 01:11:36,330
我要娶你为妻
I intend to marry you.

1114
01:11:37,020 --> 01:11:39,710
要不是我答应了我爸爸
If I hadn't promised my pa,

1115
01:11:39,960 --> 01:11:41,810
我会立马冲过这条河
hell, I'd ride on across that river right now,

1116
01:11:42,060 --> 01:11:45,630
对你父亲屈膝乞求他的同意
and on bended knee, i'd ask your daddy myself.

1117
01:11:45,930 --> 01:11:49,550
下来
Come here.

1118
01:11:49,800 --> 01:11:54,800
为娶你为妻 我不惜与世界为敌
I'd go up against the whole world to make you my wife.

1119
01:11:55,540 --> 01:11:57,800
我不能改变我的过去或者我的亲人
And I can't change my past or our kin,

1120
01:11:58,050 --> 01:12:01,530
但我告诉你
but I tell you true,

1121
01:12:01,780 --> 01:12:04,190
我从未对任何人有过这样的感觉
I ain't never felt like this before

1122
01:12:04,880 --> 01:12:09,360
直到你的出现
about nobody else but you.

1123
01:12:16,600 --> 01:12:19,170
她在那
There she is.

1124
01:12:19,420 --> 01:12:21,190
那个约翰斯・哈特菲尔德正在吻她
That's johnse Hatfield a'kissin' on her.

1125
01:12:21,440 --> 01:12:23,460
狗娘养的!
That son of a bitch!

1126
01:12:23,970 --> 01:12:25,420
你快回去吧
Now get over there.

1127
01:12:25,670 --> 01:12:26,840
你告诉他
You tell him.

1128
01:12:27,090 --> 01:12:28,740
好
Okay.

1129
01:12:34,580 --> 01:12:36,020
- 再见 - 再见
- Bye. - Bye.

1130
01:12:42,690 --> 01:12:44,190
我不敢走那座桥
I don't wanna cross that bridge.

1131
01:12:44,440 --> 01:12:46,070
我会在这看着你
I'll be here when you get back.

1132
01:12:49,060 --> 01:12:50,320
你跑不掉了 约翰斯!
Y'ain't gettin' away, johnse!

1133
01:12:50,570 --> 01:12:51,600
哦 我的天哪! 约翰斯!
Oh, my god! Johnse!

1134
01:12:52,740 --> 01:12:53,820
约翰斯 是我的兄弟们
Johnse, it's my brothers!

1135
01:12:54,070 --> 01:12:55,320
走! 快走!
Go! Go on!

1136
01:12:55,570 --> 01:12:56,790
我爱你 罗斯安娜!
I love you, roseanna!

1137
01:12:57,040 --> 01:12:57,750
驾!
Ha!

1138
01:12:58,370 --> 01:13:00,690
等等! 等等! 停!
Wait! Wait! Stop!

1139
01:13:00,940 --> 01:13:03,030
停下来! 别伤害他!
Stop! Don't hurt him!

1140
01:13:03,280 --> 01:13:05,420
他什么都没做!
He didn't do nothing!

1141
01:13:06,050 --> 01:13:07,460
巴迪 你快阻止他们!
Buddy, buddy, you gotta stop 'em!

1142
01:13:07,710 --> 01:13:09,180
爸爸让我们带你回去
We gotta get you to poppy.

1143
01:13:21,810 --> 01:13:23,050
我什么都没做!
I didn't do nothing!

1144
01:13:23,600 --> 01:13:26,820
抓住他!
Get him!

1145
01:13:27,070 --> 01:13:28,870
你死定了!
You're a dead man!

1146
01:13:35,210 --> 01:13:36,960
该死的 托尔伯特!
God damn it, tolbert!

1147
01:13:37,210 --> 01:13:39,040
你在火大什么?
What you so hot about, anyway?

1148
01:13:39,290 --> 01:13:41,410
是你扔下罗斯安娜一个人回不了家的
You're the one that left roseanna with no way home.

1149
01:13:42,080 --> 01:13:45,170
我只是为她提供了庇护所和食物
All I did was give her shelter, feed her dinner,

1150
01:13:45,550 --> 01:13:46,840
让她免受伤害!
and keep her safe from harm!

1151
01:13:47,090 --> 01:13:48,510
你用你一贯作风调戏她了?
You try to have your way with her?

1152
01:13:48,760 --> 01:13:51,070
没有 先生!
No, sir!

1153
01:13:51,320 --> 01:13:53,780
她昨晚和我妹妹们一起睡的
She spent the night with my sisters.

1154
01:13:54,030 --> 01:13:57,880
你也看见她现在安然无恙了
You saw her-safe and sound.

1155
01:13:58,130 --> 01:13:59,920
如果我强迫了她
You think she'd be kissin' on me

1156
01:14:00,170 --> 01:14:01,890
她还会吻我吗?
if I had violated her in any way?

1157
01:14:02,140 --> 01:14:02,810
我确实听到罗斯安娜说...
I did hear roseanna say...

1158
01:14:03,200 --> 01:14:04,890
闭嘴 卡尔文
Shut up, calvin.

1159
01:14:05,140 --> 01:14:06,960
我们现在杀了他 然后在被发现之前
Now, I say we kill him now and t geon back across the river

1160
01:14:07,480 --> 01:14:08,730
迅速穿过河回家
before anyone knows.

1161
01:14:08,980 --> 01:14:10,730
听着 你们妹妹知道
Hell, your sister'll know.

1162
01:14:10,980 --> 01:14:11,860
她爱我
She loves me.

1163
01:14:12,110 --> 01:14:13,610
谎话连篇 满嘴狗屎!
That's a load of bull manure!

1164
01:14:13,860 --> 01:14:14,830
不 不是
No, it ain't.

1165
01:14:15,080 --> 01:14:18,500
他妈的我也爱她 
And I love her too, god damn it.

1166
01:14:18,750 --> 01:14:22,960
看来我得证明给你们看
Since I got to prove it to you.

1167
01:14:23,210 --> 01:14:25,210
你的枪伤有多严重 约翰斯?
Well, how bad you shot, johnse?

1168
01:14:25,460 --> 01:14:28,410
这...这个...
Ha... Well...

1169
01:14:28,660 --> 01:14:29,550
我会活下来的
I'll live.

1170
01:14:30,300 --> 01:14:33,450
想想子弹都射穿了我的身体
Think the bullet tore straight through me.

1171
01:14:33,700 --> 01:14:35,820
托尔伯特 我们走
Tolbert, let's go.

1172
01:14:36,070 --> 01:14:37,920
走吧
Come on.

1173
01:14:38,430 --> 01:14:40,490
告诉你们爸爸
You tell your pa

1174
01:14:40,740 --> 01:14:43,080
我要娶罗斯安娜为妻!
I want to ask roseanna's hand in marriage!

1175
01:14:49,780 --> 01:14:50,930
嘿 爸爸! 我们找到她了!
Hey, pa! We found her!

1176
01:14:51,180 --> 01:14:52,500
我们找到她了!
We found her!

1177
01:14:52,750 --> 01:14:54,620
找到罗斯安娜了!
I got roseanna!

1178
01:15:04,230 --> 01:15:06,460
你在哈特菲尔德屋檐下过了一晚?
You spent the night under a Hatfield roof?

1179
01:15:06,710 --> 01:15:09,950
和约翰斯的妹妹们在一起
With johnse's sisters, sir.

1180
01:15:10,200 --> 01:15:11,800
哈特菲尔德先生好心收留我
Mr. Hatfield kindly gave permission.

1181
01:15:16,130 --> 01:15:20,810
约翰斯 他...他想娶我
Johnse, he, uh- He wants to marry me.

1182
01:15:23,020 --> 01:15:25,100
你说什么?
Beg your damn pardon?

1183
01:15:25,350 --> 01:15:27,800
他爱我 爸爸
He loves me, poppy.

1184
01:15:28,050 --> 01:15:30,110
他想取得你的同意
He wants to ask you proper, you know.

1185
01:15:30,360 --> 01:15:32,570
他想让一切都名正言顺
He wants to make sure it's right.

1186
01:15:35,800 --> 01:15:37,200
他碰了你 罗斯安娜?
He touch you, roseanna?

1187
01:15:37,960 --> 01:15:39,770
没有
No.

1188
01:15:47,870 --> 01:15:49,690
随便你
You go on.

1189
01:15:49,940 --> 01:15:52,100
你想做什么我都不管
Do whatever you want.

1190
01:15:52,350 --> 01:15:53,730
这么喜欢哈特菲尔德家的人
You like the Hatfields so much,

1191
01:15:53,980 --> 01:15:55,910
你干嘛不永远跟他们待在一起?
why don't you go stay with them forever?

1192
01:16:00,020 --> 01:16:01,930
从此以后我们断绝父女关系
You're not my daughter anymore.

1193
01:16:35,920 --> 01:16:37,510
你得让拉瑟福德来看看
You'll have to have rutherford take a look at this.

1194
01:16:37,760 --> 01:16:38,640
不用 没关系
No, it's fine.

1195
01:16:38,890 --> 01:16:39,640
噢!
Ow!

1196
01:16:39,890 --> 01:16:41,510
你手拿开
Keep your hand out of the way.

1197
01:16:41,760 --> 01:16:42,980
他跟你做的没什么两样
He's gonna do the same thing you're doing.

1198
01:16:43,230 --> 01:16:46,420
爸爸 她父亲没有反对
Daddy, her father don't object.

1199
01:16:46,670 --> 01:16:48,230
看起来是谁打伤了你
Well, looks like somebody did.

1200
01:16:48,480 --> 01:16:49,820
是啊 她愚蠢的兄弟们 噢!
Yeah, her boneheaded brothers-ow!

1201
01:16:50,350 --> 01:16:52,060
别动行吗?
Would you hold still?

1202
01:16:52,310 --> 01:16:53,560
我没听错吧
I want to hear again that randall McCoy

1203
01:16:53,810 --> 01:16:56,990
兰德尔・麦考伊同意把女儿嫁给你
agreed to you marrying his daughter.

1204
01:16:57,240 --> 01:16:59,760
不 不完全正确
No, not exactly.

1205
01:17:00,010 --> 01:17:02,230
他说他不在乎
He said he don't care.

1206
01:17:02,480 --> 01:17:03,570
他不在乎
He don't care.

1207
01:17:05,350 --> 01:17:07,120
"不在乎"可算不上是同意
"Don't care" ain't permission.

1208
01:17:07,370 --> 01:17:09,410
他在众人面前说的
Well, he said it in front of witnesses.

1209
01:17:10,360 --> 01:17:15,350
在你受枪伤之前还是之后 嗯?
Well, was that before or after you got shot, hmm?

1210
01:17:16,920 --> 01:17:21,080
事关他的女儿 我可不想激怒麦考伊或任何人
I will not defy McCoy or any man when it comes to his daughter.

1211
01:17:21,630 --> 01:17:23,690
爸爸 拜托了 如果你...
Daddy, please, if you...

1212
01:17:23,940 --> 01:17:24,640
如果你能同意
If you give permission,

1213
01:17:25,000 --> 01:17:26,390
他也会慢慢接受的
he'll surely come around.

1214
01:17:26,640 --> 01:17:29,130
去他妈的 孩子! 他们想杀了你!
God damn it, boy! They tried to kill you!

1215
01:17:29,380 --> 01:17:32,360
现在你还想娶个那样的?
Now you want to marry into that?

1216
01:17:32,610 --> 01:17:35,570
不是这样的
You know what? This ain't right.

1217
01:17:35,820 --> 01:17:37,280
我和她想结为夫妻...
Me and her want to be man and wife...

1218
01:17:38,450 --> 01:17:40,140
我们都到结婚的年龄了
Now, we're both of age.

1219
01:17:40,390 --> 01:17:43,920
别傻了 你才遇到她不久
Don't be a fool. You only just met her.

1220
01:17:46,530 --> 01:17:48,180
妈妈...
Mama...

1221
01:17:48,430 --> 01:17:49,870
罗斯安娜已经被赶出家门了
Roseanna's been throwed out.

1222
01:17:53,100 --> 01:17:55,500
她无处可去
She got no place to go.

1223
01:17:56,370 --> 01:17:58,380
你这是在自找罪受 孩子
You're afflicted, son.

1224
01:18:01,340 --> 01:18:06,330
好吧
All right.

1225
01:18:06,580 --> 01:18:10,170
她可以留在这等她家族来找她
She can stay here until her family comes for her

1226
01:18:10,420 --> 01:18:11,560
或者你俩恢复理智了
or you two come to your senses.

1227
01:18:11,950 --> 01:18:12,770
谢谢
Thank you.

1228
01:18:13,020 --> 01:18:16,240
谢谢你 妈妈
Thank you, mama.

1229
01:18:16,490 --> 01:18:19,400
但她要保留自己的姓
But she will keep her own name.

1230
01:18:26,800 --> 01:18:29,800
快来
Come on.

1231
01:18:33,770 --> 01:18:35,790
噢 小心那条蛇
Oh, watch out for that snake.

1232
01:18:36,140 --> 01:18:37,240
我开玩笑的
I'm just kiddin' ya.

1233
01:18:40,480 --> 01:18:42,130
我从没见过这般美景
I never knew this existed.

1234
01:18:42,380 --> 01:18:45,230
欢迎进入我的生活
Been comin' here my whole life.

1235
01:18:45,480 --> 01:18:46,870
这地方是如此美丽
It's so beautiful out here.

1236
01:18:47,120 --> 01:18:48,430
是的
Yup.

1237
01:18:54,860 --> 01:18:56,690
你在干什么?
What are you doin'?

1238
01:19:05,490 --> 01:19:08,760
我的天 约翰斯 你疯了
Oh, my-you are crazy, Johnse.

1239
01:19:15,770 --> 01:19:17,820
来和我一起戏水吧
Come get in the water with me.

1240
01:19:18,070 --> 01:19:19,990
在这里?
Out here?

1241
01:19:20,240 --> 01:19:21,670
在上帝的眼皮底下?
In the eyes of god?

1242
01:19:22,110 --> 01:19:24,700
反对我们的又不是上帝
God didn't forbid our union.

1243
01:19:24,950 --> 01:19:28,070
是我们的父亲
Our fathers did.

1244
01:19:28,320 --> 01:19:32,060
上帝知道在我们心中 彼此早已成婚
God knows we're married in our hearts.

1245
01:19:32,310 --> 01:19:33,430
来吧
Come on.

1246
01:20:17,500 --> 01:20:22,050
待会见 好吗?
See you later, all right?

1247
01:20:22,300 --> 01:20:23,560
什么事?
What's the matter?

1248
01:20:23,810 --> 01:20:26,340
哈特菲尔德亲戚
Hatfield kin.

1249
01:20:29,210 --> 01:20:30,450
普莱恩错了
Plain ain't right.

1250
01:20:31,250 --> 01:20:34,870
一年多了 罗斯安娜还住在哈特菲尔德家里
Over a year now Roseanna's livin' under the Hatfield roof,

1251
01:20:35,120 --> 01:20:36,240
脱掉裙子 然后摇身变成
droppin' her skirt and turnin' out to be

1252
01:20:36,490 --> 01:20:38,200
任宰任割的鱼肉
just a steady piece of cake.

1253
01:20:38,450 --> 01:20:40,110
这一定让哈特菲尔德那老头
Must make old man Hatfield

1254
01:20:40,360 --> 01:20:42,170
快活得像只鸡舍里的公鸡
happier'n a banty rooster in a henhouse,

1255
01:20:42,420 --> 01:20:45,880
那让我们家族蒙羞
having our family so disgraced.

1256
01:20:46,130 --> 01:20:48,000
是的
Yup.

1257
01:20:54,940 --> 01:20:55,820
有何贵干?
Help ya?

1258
01:20:56,070 --> 01:20:57,020
我是弗兰克・菲利普斯
Frank Phillips.

1259
01:20:57,670 --> 01:21:00,630
在肯塔基州路易斯维尔镇平克顿办公室做事
Work outta the Pinkerton office, Pouisville, Kentucky.

1260
01:21:00,880 --> 01:21:03,060
我在找鲍勃・莱温格
Lookin' for Bob Levinger.

1261
01:21:03,310 --> 01:21:05,710
轮班时没看见鲍勃
Ain't seen Bob in a spell.

1262
01:21:08,720 --> 01:21:10,640
要是对一个平克顿的 
A fella could get himself into a lot of trouble

1263
01:21:10,890 --> 01:21:12,740
持有美国副检察官证的人撒谎
lyin' to a Pinkerton man

1264
01:21:13,090 --> 01:21:16,620
那人会惹上一身腥的
with a US Deputy prosecutor warrant.

1265
01:21:16,870 --> 01:21:20,950
这足以构成犯罪了
It makes it a federal offense.

1266
01:21:21,200 --> 01:21:25,790
我们可以谈谈监狱和罚金
So we're talkin' prison, a big fine.

1267
01:21:26,040 --> 01:21:28,890
有人会失去他的小酒馆
A feller could lose his saloon,

1268
01:21:29,140 --> 01:21:33,230
以及所有打拼来的东西
everything he's slaved for.

1269
01:21:33,480 --> 01:21:36,960
等出狱时 他就是个穷光蛋
Time he's outta jail, he's dead broke.

1270
01:21:37,210 --> 01:21:41,770
老婆和某个花心的投机家跑了
His wife's run off with some dandy carpetbagger.

1271
01:21:42,120 --> 01:21:47,040
我见过这种事
I seen it happen.

1272
01:21:47,290 --> 01:21:50,240
那个玩纸牌的光头
Playin' cards, bald one.

1273
01:22:02,200 --> 01:22:04,460
鲍勃・莱温格
Bob levinger.

1274
01:22:04,710 --> 01:22:06,460
你没有房屋居住证
You got no paper on where you're livin'.

1275
01:22:07,240 --> 01:22:10,430
房子违章搭建 也没缴税
Squatter, payin' no taxes.

1276
01:22:10,680 --> 01:22:14,900
书信警告过两次 其中一次是联邦官员发出的
You've been warned twice by mail, once by federal officer.

1277
01:22:15,150 --> 01:22:17,970
你得跟我走一趟
I'm here to take you in.

1278
01:22:18,220 --> 01:22:21,170
这是拘捕令
This here's a warrant.

1279
