1450
01:33:33,640 --> 01:33:36,310
赶紧的 我刚刚说过
Go on. That's what I said.

1451
01:33:41,510 --> 01:33:43,110
噢!
Oh!

1452
01:33:47,650 --> 01:33:50,670
我知道你是谁 你长得有点像她
I know who you are, 'cause you look like her, kind of.

1453
01:33:50,920 --> 01:33:52,790
驾!
Yah!

1454
01:34:06,640 --> 01:34:08,470
罗斯安娜的堂姐南茜
Roseanna's cousin nancy.

1455
01:34:14,410 --> 01:34:18,810
和晚上相比 现在你看起来
You-you kind of look like roseanna in the daylight too.

1456
01:34:22,820 --> 01:34:25,570
要更像罗斯安娜一些
More at night, though.

1457
01:34:25,820 --> 01:34:30,810
我昨天拜访了我姑妈贝蒂・布兰肯希普一家
I went and visited my aunt betty blankenship's yesterday.

1458
01:34:31,200 --> 01:34:33,830
我猜你知道你的未婚妻待在那里
I suppose you know your once-intended is stayin' there.

1459
01:34:34,700 --> 01:34:35,870
我不知道
No.

1460
01:34:37,630 --> 01:34:39,750
估计老家伙还在为她和我
Guess the old man's still riled

1461
01:34:40,000 --> 01:34:44,020
使家族蒙羞而暴跳如雷
at how me and her shamed his family.

1462
01:34:44,270 --> 01:34:49,260
对啊 尤其是罗斯安娜还怀孕了
Well, especially now that roseanna's with child and all.

1463
01:34:49,810 --> 01:34:51,650
什么?
What?

1464
01:34:54,950 --> 01:34:58,970
我要做爸爸了?
I'm gonna be a daddy?

1465
01:34:59,480 --> 01:35:01,010
就因为她怀孕了
Because she carries his child,

1466
01:35:01,260 --> 01:35:03,720
罗斯安娜觉得自己爱上了约翰斯・哈特菲尔德
roseanna believes herself in love with johnse Hatfield.

1467
01:35:04,790 --> 01:35:06,990
爸爸知道这事了吗?
Does our pap know about this?

1468
01:35:07,240 --> 01:35:08,880
就他现在的身体状况 
Strong as he is,

1469
01:35:08,880 --> 01:35:11,020
我担心这事会要了你老头的命
I fear it may break your father's heart.

1470
01:35:11,270 --> 01:35:12,610
在他发现之前 
Shame we can't remedy the situation

1471
01:35:12,610 --> 01:35:15,890
我们一点补救措施都没有 真特么丧气
before he finds out.

1472
01:35:16,140 --> 01:35:17,790
如果没有约翰斯
If it weren't for johnse,

1473
01:35:18,040 --> 01:35:19,160
罗斯安娜也许能保持理智
roseanna might come to her senses

1474
01:35:19,410 --> 01:35:22,760
接受订好的婚约
and accept an offer of honorable marriage.

1475
01:35:23,010 --> 01:35:25,170
- 咱们走 - 赶紧的
- Let's go. - Come on.

1476
01:35:25,650 --> 01:35:27,800
嗨...
Hey...

1477
01:35:28,050 --> 01:35:29,630
你们要干嘛?
What are you doing?

1478
01:35:30,390 --> 01:35:31,400
孩子们
Boys.

1479
01:35:32,260 --> 01:35:33,100
孩子们!
Boys!

1480
01:35:33,350 --> 01:35:35,190
你们这是要去哪儿啊?
Where are you going?

1481
01:35:54,640 --> 01:35:57,100
很好...
Well...

1482
01:35:57,350 --> 01:36:01,030
我正想找你们
Just the boys I wanna see.

1483
01:36:01,280 --> 01:36:04,270
咱们可以一起去你们姑妈贝蒂家
You can ride with me to your aunt betty's house.

1484
01:36:04,520 --> 01:36:06,840
我要去那儿解救我的新娘
I'm going there to rescue my bride,

1485
01:36:07,090 --> 01:36:08,300
给她一个名分
make an honest woman of her.

1486
01:36:08,550 --> 01:36:10,510
闭上你的狗嘴!
Just you shut the hell up!

1487
01:36:10,760 --> 01:36:12,550
少来你这套骗人的把戏
You ain't lyin' your way out of it this time.

1488
01:36:12,800 --> 01:36:14,280
我没骗人
I ain't lying.

1489
01:36:14,530 --> 01:36:19,120
我才得知罗斯安娜怀了我的孩子
Just found out roseanna's carrying my baby.

1490
01:36:19,370 --> 01:36:21,290
所以我立马赶去找她
So I'm going to get her,

1491
01:36:21,540 --> 01:36:24,690
咱老爸看到肯定会气得冒烟
seeing as how our daddies are being such horses' asses.

1492
01:36:28,810 --> 01:36:31,930
你死定了 哈特菲尔德 你别想活着离开!
You're dead, Hatfield. You're gonna be dead!

1493
01:36:32,180 --> 01:36:34,070
别碰我 托尔伯特!
Get off of me, tolbert!

1494
01:36:34,320 --> 01:36:36,270
你为啥要跟你未来的妹夫过不去?
Why you want to hurt your future brother-in-law?

1495
01:36:36,520 --> 01:36:38,910
我要杀了你 你毁了我妹妹的清白!
I'm gonna kill you, 'cause you soiled my sister's honor!

1496
01:36:39,160 --> 01:36:40,960
我都说了 我要和她结婚!
I told you, i'm gonna marry her!

1497
01:36:58,410 --> 01:37:02,230
卡尔文?
Calvin?

1498
01:37:02,480 --> 01:37:04,960
兰德尔?
Randall?

1499
01:37:05,210 --> 01:37:06,970
你在干嘛?
What's-what are you doing?

1500
01:37:07,220 --> 01:37:08,830
爱丽菲尔 让孩子们回房间
Alifair, get the kids back.

1501
01:37:09,080 --> 01:37:11,150
快 快啊!
Git. Git!

1502
01:37:11,790 --> 01:37:13,240
你这是干嘛?
What are you doin'?

1503
01:37:13,780 --> 01:37:16,170
你喝醉了?
Are you drunk?

1504
01:37:16,420 --> 01:37:19,870
你打算瞒着我 对吧?
You weren't gonna tell me, were ya?

1505
01:37:20,120 --> 01:37:23,820
我听佩里・克莱因说了
I had to hear it from Perry Cline.

1506
01:37:24,070 --> 01:37:25,680
停下 那是罗斯安娜的嫁妆箱
Well, stop. That's roseanna's hope chest.

1507
01:37:25,930 --> 01:37:26,690
停下来!
Stop!

1508
01:37:26,940 --> 01:37:28,170
我知道是里面装的是什么!
I know what it is!

1509
01:37:36,080 --> 01:37:38,350
估计你在奇怪我为什么没直接要你小命
Suppose you's wonderin' why I don't kill you straight away.

1510
01:37:38,600 --> 01:37:40,720
因为你知道这样做不对
'Cause you know it ain't right.

1511
01:37:40,970 --> 01:37:42,730
放狗屁!
Horseshit!

1512
01:37:42,980 --> 01:37:47,110
就像在部队里一样
I'm gonna blow your brains out exactly at sunrise,

1513
01:37:47,360 --> 01:37:49,940
天一亮 我就一枪崩了你
like they do in the army.

1514
01:37:50,190 --> 01:37:51,980
我就是要你眼睁睁的等死
See, I want you to know it's comin'.

1515
01:37:52,230 --> 01:37:55,830
我要你一直被恐惧折磨
And I want you to think about it for all those hours!

1516
01:37:57,070 --> 01:37:58,380
让你也尝尝
Feel the kind of torment

1517
01:37:58,630 --> 01:38:00,580
你和哈特菲尔德家族的人给我们带来的痛苦
you and all the Hatfields have brought down on us.

1518
01:38:00,830 --> 01:38:04,560
我是尊重你妹妹的 托尔伯特
I respect your sister, tolbert.

1519
01:38:04,810 --> 01:38:07,230
你知道的
You know that.

1520
01:38:07,480 --> 01:38:10,660
更何况她现在怀有我的骨肉
Especially now that she's carrying my baby.

1521
01:38:11,340 --> 01:38:13,210
让我去找个牧师来主持我和她的婚礼
Let me go find a preacher and make it legal.

1522
01:38:13,460 --> 01:38:15,090
现在说这些太晚了!
Well, it's too late for that!

1523
01:38:15,340 --> 01:38:16,940
黎明时分 就是你的死期
I'm gonna shoot you dead come dawn,

1524
01:38:17,190 --> 01:38:19,640
我会整点报时
and I'm gonna tell you what time it is

1525
01:38:19,890 --> 01:38:22,640
让你知道你离死神越来越近!
every hour we get closer!

1526
01:38:25,590 --> 01:38:29,400
我死前能提最后一个请求吗?
Instead of a last meal, can I-can I get a last request?

1527
01:38:29,650 --> 01:38:32,080
去你妈的 不行!
Hell, no!

1528
01:38:32,330 --> 01:38:33,690
你想要什么?
What do you want?

1529
01:38:33,940 --> 01:38:36,760
我想见罗斯安娜最后一面
I want to see roseanna one last time.

1530
01:38:37,010 --> 01:38:39,700
我想郑重跟她说一声再见
I want to say good-bye to her in a proper way.

1531
01:38:40,510 --> 01:38:43,130
我向天发誓
And then I will stand up tall when you shoot me.

1532
01:38:43,380 --> 01:38:46,630
之后我会站直让你枪杀我
I swear to god I will.

1533
01:38:46,880 --> 01:38:48,600
等我去了天堂
And when I get to heaven,

1534
01:38:48,850 --> 01:38:50,300
我不会诅咒你的灵魂
I won't damn your souls

1535
01:38:50,550 --> 01:38:52,270
我会向上帝请求不要
and ask god to send you fryin' to hell

1536
01:38:52,520 --> 01:38:54,210
把你送去地狱受惩罚
for what you done to me.

1537
01:38:55,990 --> 01:38:58,040
你才是要下地狱的人
You're the one going to hell,

1538
01:38:58,490 --> 01:39:03,450
你没有资格在上帝面前提要求
and you ain't gonna be askin' god for squat.

1539
01:39:04,500 --> 01:39:06,150
罗斯安娜是爱他的
Roseanna does love him.

1540
01:39:06,400 --> 01:39:08,350
我们要是不这么做 她会恨我们一辈子的
She'll hate us forever if we don't allow it.

1541
01:39:08,600 --> 01:39:10,480
不行 我说过了!
No, I said!

1542
01:39:11,640 --> 01:39:13,390
除了一碗汤
He gets a bowl of stew.

1543
01:39:13,640 --> 01:39:15,990
其他的都别想要
Nothing else.

1544
01:39:16,240 --> 01:39:18,660
我不喜欢喝汤
That stew didn't set right with me.

1545
01:39:18,910 --> 01:39:20,000
你们介意我回家吗?
Do y'all mind if I go home?

1546
01:39:20,250 --> 01:39:22,200
当然 兄弟
No, sure, bud.

1547
01:39:22,450 --> 01:39:24,140
来吧
Come on.

1548
01:39:24,390 --> 01:39:26,290
我们开杀戒的时候 你最好不在场
You shouldn't be here when we do the killin' anyways.

1549
01:39:26,540 --> 01:39:28,160
对 你太小了
Yeah, you're too young.

1550
01:39:28,660 --> 01:39:30,510
我不小了
I ain't too young.

1551
01:39:30,760 --> 01:39:32,960
我就是觉得不舒服 好吗?
I just don't feel so good, all right?

1552
01:39:35,230 --> 01:39:37,450
拜了 兄弟
Bye, bud.

1553
01:39:37,700 --> 01:39:39,430
该死的 我在阴间等你
Hell, I'll see you on the other side.

1554
01:40:22,300 --> 01:40:23,260
我要跟我妹讲话
I got to talk to my sister.

1555
01:40:23,510 --> 01:40:24,860
噢 天啊 兄弟
Oh, my god, bud.

1556
01:40:25,110 --> 01:40:26,760
你这是干什么去了?
What are you doing out in this?

1557
01:40:33,290 --> 01:40:34,420
哈特菲尔德先生!
Mr. Hatfield!

1558
01:40:36,290 --> 01:40:38,230
哈特菲尔德先生!
Mr. Hatfield!

1559
01:40:40,560 --> 01:40:42,400
哈特菲尔德先生!
Mr. Hatfield!

1560
01:40:46,700 --> 01:40:48,950
我的兄弟们抓住了约翰斯!
My brothers have got johnse!

1561
01:40:49,200 --> 01:40:51,460
他们准备天亮时分杀了他!
They're plannin' on killin' him at dawn!

1562
01:40:51,710 --> 01:40:52,580
他在哪儿?
Where is he?

1563
01:40:53,370 --> 01:40:54,990
如果我告诉你 你发誓
If I tell you, you got to swear

1564
01:40:55,240 --> 01:40:56,600
不要伤害我的兄弟们!
you ain't gonna hurt my brothers!

1565
01:40:56,850 --> 01:41:00,030
只要我儿子无恙 你的兄弟们肯定没事
If my son is safe, no harm will come to your brothers.

1566
01:41:00,280 --> 01:41:01,550
说 他在哪儿?
Now, where is he?

1567
01:41:02,180 --> 01:41:04,000
他们在我叔叔哈蒙家的老房子
They got him at my uncle harmon's old place.

1568
01:41:04,250 --> 01:41:05,220
走 走 走 快走
Go, go, go, go, go.

1569
01:41:05,470 --> 01:41:07,390
哈特菲尔德先生 拜托你 要快!
Please, Mr. Hatfield, hurry!

1570
01:41:07,640 --> 01:41:09,520
赶快 我去给你拿靴子
Go on. I'll get your boots.

1571
01:41:09,770 --> 01:41:10,930
拜托!
Please!

1572
01:41:14,360 --> 01:41:16,980
约翰斯 我们暂时不会了结你小命
Now, johnse, we wouldn't normally kill you,

1573
01:41:17,670 --> 01:41:19,780
直到有一位绅士光明正大的迎娶我妹妹
'cept there's an honorable man willing to marry our sister

1574
01:41:20,030 --> 01:41:21,150
那时才是你的死期
soon as you're dead.

1575
01:41:24,270 --> 01:41:27,260
是谁?
Who's that?

1576
01:41:27,910 --> 01:41:31,430
佩里・克莱因律师答应迎娶罗斯安娜
Lawyer Perry Cline has agreed to make roseanna his wife.

1577
01:41:31,680 --> 01:41:35,500
杀夫夺子 还要霸占别人的妻子
Having a man killed to marry their woman and take their baby,

1578
01:41:35,750 --> 01:41:37,380
这可不是光明正大行为
that ain't honorable.

1579
01:41:37,630 --> 01:41:40,050
还剩一小时 哈特菲尔德
One hour to go, Hatfield.

